WEBVTT

00:00:01.040 --> 00:00:03.456
Do you remember when you were a child,

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:07.056
you probably had a favorite toy
that was a constant companion,

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:09.696
like Christopher Robin
had Winnie the Pooh,

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:12.520
and your imagination
fueled endless adventures?

00:00:13.640 --> 00:00:16.040
What could be more innocent than that?

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:21.600
Well, let me introduce you
to my friend Cayla.

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:26.056
Cayla was voted toy of the year
in countries around the world.

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:29.656
She connects to the internet
and uses speech recognition technology

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:31.816
to answer your child's questions,